description: The Transferpette® S Single-Channel / Fixed Pipette, 100 µL, BRAND, F-100 model is the perfect manual pipette for demanding laboratory scientists with intensive ergonomic and innovative materials. It offers robust yet lightweight construction, superior autoclavability, one-handed operation, high degree of accuracy and precision and long lasting reliability. This pipette can be applied for research, diagnotic, and clinical pipetting.
name: S Single-Channel or Fixed Pipette
